data.description: Welcome to your dream home in sought after Kingwood. This 4 bd, 2.5 bth boasts all the features you could want in a home. With 2704 sf ft of living space, home also features a game room and study, perfect for those who work from home or love to entertain guests. Backyard is an oasis, complete with patio and sprinkler system to keep the lawn lush and green. You'll love to spend time outside with family and friends, enjoying the beautiful Texas weather. Home is move in ready, new roof installed 2019, new fence 2018. Never flooded. Located on quiet cul-de-sac, this home will offer you peace and privacy while still being close to all the amenities Kingwood has to offer. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours. Contact me to schedule your private showing.
